name: Winston's Fall
description:
Winsonton fell out of his spacship. Use the left and right arrow keys on your keyboard to manouver around.

Collect as many stars as possible!

Collecting a bubble gives you a buffer for 10 Seconds. You are able to defeat enemies if you collide with them while you are in a bubble. Defeating an enemie gives you additional points!

Read more about this project on my blog.

http://www.milikdblog.wordpress.com
